Package: spatialfil
Type: Package
Title: Package for applying 2D convolution kernel filters to matrices or arrays
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-09-08
Author: Nicola Dinapoli
Maintainer: Nicola Dinapoli <nicola.dinapoli@rm.unicatt.it>
Description: This package is aimed to filtering two (or three) dimensional data using different convolution kernels.
  By the moment only Gaussian and Laplacian of Gaussian (LoG) kernels have been implemented
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), abind